git remote add origin https://github.com/Bob789/Final_Project_v003.git#| File/Folder              | Description                                                   |
#| ------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
#| `.env`                   | Prevents exposure of passwords or API keys                    |
#| `.venv/`, `venv/`        | Skips Python virtual environment files                        |
#| `__pycache__/`           | Prevents storing automatically compiled Python files          |
#| `.idea/`, `.vscode/`     | Excludes IDE configuration files (such as PyCharm or VS Code) |
#| `*.log`, `*.tmp`         | Ignores log and temporary files                               |
#| `.DS_Store`, `Thumbs.db` | Ignores system files created by macOS and Windows             |

